Package: rosario
Title: An Algorithm to Analyze Cyclical Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ángel L.", "Robles-Fernández", , "a.l.robles.fernandez@gmail.com", role = c("aut"))
    person("Maria A.", "Hurtado-Materon", , "maria.h.m_1995@tamu.edu", role = c("aut"))
    person("Tatiana", "Velásquez-Roa", , "yxh11@txstate.edu", role = c("aut"))
    person("Iván", "Castro-Arellano", , "ic13@txstate.edu", role = c("ths", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to quantify and visualize temporal niche overlap among biological identities (species, populations, or other units) using indices (Pianka, Czekanowski) and null models. The package implements the ROSARIO algorithm (Castro-Arellano et al. 2010) <doi:10.1111/j.2041-210X.2010.00031.x>.
